ZH: 我收集邮票。
EN: I collect stamps.

ZH: 他买了一套邮票。
EN: He bought a set of stamps.

ZH: 她喜欢买不同国家的邮票。
EN: She likes to buy stamps from different countries.

ZH: 我的邮票收藏品很有价值。
EN: My stamp collection is very valuable.

ZH: 你愿意跟我交换邮票吗？
EN: Would you like to exchange stamps with me?

ZH: 我的朋友送给我一张邮票。
EN: My friend gave me a stamp.

ZH: 我从邮局买了一本邮票册。
EN: I bought a stamp book from the post office.

ZH: 这枚邮票是2010年发行的。
EN: This stamp was issued in 2010.

ZH: 这些邮票很漂亮。
EN: These stamps are very beautiful.

ZH: 我们去邮局买邮票吧。
EN: Let's go to the post office to buy stamps.

ZH: 我的爷爷有一大箱邮票。
EN: My grandfather has a big box of stamps.

ZH: 我的宝藏是一些古老邮票。
EN: My treasure is some old stamps.

ZH: 这个邮票有纪念意义。
EN: This stamp has commemorative significance.

ZH: 我需要邮票寄明信片。
EN: I need stamps to mail postcards.

ZH: 我们可以买一些邮票寄信。
EN: We can buy some stamps to mail letters.

ZH: 他的梦想是拥有全世界各地的邮票。
EN: His dream is to have stamps from all over the world.

ZH: 那些邮票值得一大笔钱。
EN: Those stamps are worth a lot of money.

ZH: 我喜欢在信封上贴邮票。
EN: I like to put stamps on envelopes.

ZH: 这些邮票都是特别纪念邮票。
EN: These stamps are all special commemorative stamps.

ZH: 我要去邮局买邮票寄信。
EN: I am going to the post office to buy stamps to mail letters.
